Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thật không?!{Really?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứu với...{Help...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tớ nghe thấy rồi!{I heard it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứu với...{Help...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứu với...{Help...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Người nằm dưới đất kia là một nhà thám hiểm!{Down on the ground there... It's a cave raider!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Để tớ đuổi nó đi.{I'll drive that thing away.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứu với... Cứu...{Help me... Help...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, khoan đã!
