Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bình tĩnh...{Calm down...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Không được phép trượt!{I can't miss this!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chết rồi!{This is bad!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi lên cao ở Abyss sẽ bị...!{Ở Abyss mà đi lên cao sẽ bị...! {Lên cao ở Abyss cũng đồng nghĩa với...!{Ascending within the Abyss means...!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Xa quá!{Too far!}
