Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,May quá đi! { rồi!{I'm glad you're awake!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu không tỉnh lại làm tớ lo muốn chết!{You wouldn't wake up, so I got really worried!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A, nhưng cậu nên nằm xuống đã...{Ah, but... you should stay lying down for now...}
